P3DFFT VERSION 2.3

(c) Dmitry Pekurovsky, 2008

RELEASE NOTES

New in Version 2.3:

- Bug fixes
- More example programs added, including in-place transform and power spectrum
- C interface provided
- Examples in C are now available in addition to Fortran. 
- Building the library and examples are made easier by including platform-specific makefiles
- List of platforms expanded to include Ranger (Sun/AMD at TACC) and Kraken (Cray XT4 at ORNL)
